  },
  {
    question: "Are there watermarks or sign-up required?",
    answer: "No watermarks ever. No account or sign-up needed. All tools are free to use."
  },
  {
    question: "How fast are the conversions?",
    answer: "Client-side tools are instant. Backend conversions are optimized and typically complete in seconds."
  },
  {
    question: "What file sizes are supported?",
    answer: "Most tools support up to 150MB files, allowing you to work with large documents easily."
  },
  {
    question: "Is PDFEliteTools really free?",
    answer: "Most tools are available for free. No sign-up required. Start using our PDF tools instantly without creating an account."
  },
